      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, 35% increase in cognitive function? That sounds massive. I thought the primary endpoint for the Phase II trial was supposed to be the neuro-cognitive score improvement across the whole cohort. Looking back at my notes, I was under the impression the overall p-value was actually non-significant. Can you double check the primary endpoint data for me? I don't want to get blindsided by the board if they ask about the total sample size.",
